 R&amp;F - Jiangsu Suning</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1587","checkdouble":"191947"},{"date":"06:49 25/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng 1/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-robin-olsen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn 1/8 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Alisson Becker, AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robin Olsen t\u1eeb Copenhagen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1n Alisson Becker cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 72.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, AS Roma kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Robin Olsen t\u1eeb FC Copenhagen (\u0110an M\u1ea1ch) v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 3.5 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-robin-olsen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFC Copenhagen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 10% gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p AS Roma b\u00e1n Olsen trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai/ \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e3i to c\u1ee7a AS Roma khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao khi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Robin Olsen cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robin Olsen l\u00e0 ai?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Malmo (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n), Olsen g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khung g\u1ed7 FC Copenhagen \u1edf ba m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. Olsen ra m\u1eaft \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1/2015 v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 23 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a AS Roma chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y: \"Robin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Roma. T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Olsen \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch hai l\u1ea7n, v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch hai l\u1ea7n. T\u1ea1i AS Roma, Olsen s\u1ebd mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a AS Roma:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech-172-191845.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\">M\u1ea5t Alisson, s\u1ebfp Roma v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-the-gay-soc-vu-alisson-chelsea-chuyen-huong-sang-donnarumma-172-191596.html\">Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i thay Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi \u201cbi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t\u201d t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1586","checkdouble":"191948"},{"date":"16:03 24/07","title":"Leroy Sane: \u201cCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/leroy-sane-danh-gia-cao-chelsea-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Leroy-Sane-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi th\u00eam 140 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus, bao g\u1ed3m: Trung v\u1ec7 Rugani, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Higuain v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pjanic.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane phat bieu ve Chelsea\" title=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/leroy-sane-danh-gia-cao-chelsea-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1ch Napoli ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecd \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Sarri s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t HLV th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Perth Glory v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Pedro. \u1ede tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/perth-glory-vs-chelsea-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191830.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea 1-0 Perth Glory</span>, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 cho ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Jorginho, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1585","checkdouble":"191919"},{"date":"16:24 24/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/vidal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayern Munich trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arturo Vidal \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 25 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Vidal \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi \"H\u00f9m x\u00e1m\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/MU-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-26-trieu-bang-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Vidal s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Chile El Mercurio, Vidal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Bayern Munich \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fernando Felicevich c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Vidal mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Leon Goretzka t\u1eeb Schalke v\u00e0 g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Renato Sanches, t\u00e2n HLV Niko\u00a0Kovac s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Vidal n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Bayern y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Vidal, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t. Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e1u l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU co kha nang rat lon chieu mo thanh cong Vidal\" title=\"MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Theo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-mourinho-muon-xin-them-kinh-phi-de-nang-cap-2-vi-tri-172-191893.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p th\u00eam 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span> \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Bayern \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. Ngo\u00e0i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u00ec Inter Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford. Vidal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mourinho. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1584","checkdouble":"191920"},{"date":"16:04 24/07","title":"Mahrez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mahrez-tiet-lo-tham-vong-lon-sau-khi-gia-nhap-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>San Jose Earthquakes hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i MLS. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn l\u1eafm m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/170116-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man United kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Man United t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 571 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 85%. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Martial, Sanchez v\u00e0 Chong tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian khi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, qu\u00e3ng chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhanh nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man United. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u00e0y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i t\u0103m l\u00e0 Matteo Darmian. N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 Fosu-Mensah, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes</span> ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Pogba th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t khi thi\u1ebfu Lukaku\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba va Lukaku\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Nhan-dinh-co-hoi-MU-vo-dich-giai-Ngoai-hang-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Lukaku</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man United trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tay s\u0103n b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. V\u1eady n\u00ean m\u1ed7i khi thi\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao cao to ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng gi\u00fap MU thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n sau khi gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i MLS. Nh\u01b0ng ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, Sanchez h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 HLV Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n. C\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial\" title=\"Anthony Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Wayne-Rooney-khuyen-MU-giu-chan-Martial-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a khi \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Martial nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec Man United. \u0110\u1ea7u \u00f3c c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c sau khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford. V\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Martial \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y th\u00ec kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u00ean l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Man United. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Sanchez kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Martial c\u0169ng g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-arturo-vidal-sap-ky-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-191920.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-247-187-191902.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 24/7: M.U ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua trung v\u1ec7 Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1583","checkdouble":"191921"},{"date":"16:19 24/07","title":"C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c thi vi\u1ebft \"\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/cong-bo-ket-qua-cuoc-thi-viet-an-tuong-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cu\u1ed9c thi vi\u1ebft \"\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018\" d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 trang Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nga, BBT ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/KQ-WC18-600.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1eady l\u00e0, World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0 v\u1ecb kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean cho c\u00e1c fan  h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9c  gi\u1ea3 trang Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi World  Cup n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua n\u00f3i chung, BBT Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cu\u1ed9c  thi vi\u1ebft &quot;\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018&quot;. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft,  trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt b\u00e0i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c b\u1edfi c\u00e1c tay vi\u1ebft b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1  chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau th\u1eddi gian r\u00e0 so\u00e1t v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t  s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 trao th\u01b0\u1edfng. Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I NH\u1ea4T (5 tri\u1ec7u VN\u0110)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nWorld Cup v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/world-cup-va-nhung-bat-ngo-471-191342.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/world-cup-va-nhung-bat-ngo-471-191342.html</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I NH\u00cc (2 tri\u1ec7u VN\u0110/gi\u1ea3i)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng&rdquo; ngay t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/co-mot-san-van-dong-ngay-tai-benh-vien-471-191476.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/co-mot-san-van-dong-ngay-tai-benh-vien-471-191476.html</span><br>\r\n2. Th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Neymar - C\u1eadu h\u00e3y tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-neymar-cau-hay-truong-thanh-hon-471-190724.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-neymar-cau-hay-truong-thanh-hon-471-190724.html</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I BA (1 tri\u1ec7u VN\u0110/gi\u1ea3i)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n1. Ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, B\u1ed3 \u01a1i<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tien-len-bo-oi-471-190447.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tien-len-bo-oi-471-190447.html</span><br>\r\n2. Sinh nh\u1eadt Messi, Ronaldo g\u1eedi th\u01b0 nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/sinh-nhat-messi-ronaldo-gui-thu-nhan-nhucau-chi-la-doi-thu-thu-hai-471-189497.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/sinh-nhat-messi-ronaldo-gui-thu-nhan-nhucau-chi-la-doi-thu-thu-hai-471-189497.html</span><br>\r\n3. C\u01a1n m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; tr\u00ean m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea5p b\u1ed1n!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/con-mua-gach-da-tren-mai-nha-cap-bon-471-190194.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/con-mua-gach-da-tren-mai-nha-cap-bon-471-190194.html</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I KHUY\u1ebeN KH\u00cdCH (500.000 VN\u0110/gi\u1ea3i)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n1. Lionel Messi, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, m\u00e0u anh ch\u1ecdn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u00e0u d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-wc-lionel-messi-sau-tat-ca-mau-anh-chon-van-la-mau-dan-toc-471-191125.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-wc-lionel-messi-sau-tat-ca-mau-anh-chon-van-la-mau-dan-toc-471-191125.html</span><br>\r\n2. B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00f2n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-hoc-tu-trai-bong-tron-471-191032.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-hoc-tu-trai-bong-tron-471-191032.html</span><br>\r\n3. Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa l\u00ean, h\u1ee1i nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-nhay-mua-len-hoi-nhung-vu-cong-huyen-thoai-471-189035.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-nhay-mua-len-hoi-nhung-vu-cong-huyen-thoai-471-189035.html</span><br>\r\n4. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb Anh - Edison Cavani<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/toi-nho-anh-471-190929.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/toi-nho-anh-471-190929.html</span><br>\r\n5. Th\u00e2n g\u1eedi Messi, th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/than-gui-messi-than-tuong-cua-toi-471-189483.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/than-gui-messi-than-tuong-cua-toi-471-189483.html</span><br>\r\n6. Th\u01a1 t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tho-tong-ket-world-cup-2018-471-191589.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tho-tong-ket-world-cup-2018-471-191589.html</span><br>\r\n7. Th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Kasper: Cha t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 con!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-kasper-cha-tu-hao-ve-con-471-190335.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-kasper-cha-tu-hao-ve-con-471-190335.html</span><br>\r\n8. Croatia - \u0110\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam <br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/croatia-dau-do-bong-dang-u23-viet-nam-471-191366.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/croatia-dau-do-bong-dang-u23-viet-nam-471-191366.html</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c thi nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ec7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 n\u00e0o ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft trong danh s\u00e1ch tr\u00fang gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u1ec7t k\u00ea ph\u00eda tr\u00ean vi ph\u1ea1m th\u1ec3 l\u1ec7 (nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hay sao ch\u00e9p, x\u00e0o n\u1ea5u c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c) th\u00ec vui l\u00f2ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u1ea1i cho BTC qua \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email <strong>gocbandoc@bongda24h.vn</strong>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi x\u00e1c minh n\u1ebfu l\u1eddi khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao gi\u1ea3i cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft vi ph\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01a1n. Sau m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i n\u00e0o, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh trao gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXin tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 Bongda24h.vn cho cu\u1ed9c thi vi\u1ebft &quot;\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1582","checkdouble":"191922"},{"date":"16:52 24/07","title":"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \"gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m\" m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-muc-tieu-gia-mem-ma-real-madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi chia tay Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn 'gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m' h\u01a1n cho Real.</h2><h2>3. Anthony Martial</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed3i cho Real trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho song Martial v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp ghi nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 31 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 131 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Martial song v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Wayne Rooney, Martial l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 Ander Herrera c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng anh th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/3-muc-tieu-ma-Real-Madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Martial s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn '\u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n' v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau tuy nhi\u00ean hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Do v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Real nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 Man United.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Chelsea, Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial nh\u01b0ng HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Real Madrid. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Martial m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Sadio Mane</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Mohamed Salah, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sadio Mane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, Mane lu\u00f4n cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng The Kop/\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Liverpool tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Mane lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Real ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Zidane \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac khi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean Mane v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Real. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Mane ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span> th\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah va Mane\" title=\"Salah va Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/liverpool-toi-my-du-dau-tam-tau-ke-o-nguoi-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Mane r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>1. Ivan Perisic</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. V\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, Perisic lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c th\u1eeba. Trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c x\u00e9 toang h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic la tru cot cua Inter\" title=\"Ivan Perisic la tru cot cua Inter\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Ivan-Perisic-la-tru-cot-cua-Inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i\u00a0Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, m\u1ed7i khi x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp trung l\u1ed9, Perisic th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi anh lu\u00f4n l\u00f9i s\u00e2u tranh ch\u1ea5p khu gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Perisic ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t 'm\u00f3n h\u1eddi' cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Eden Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-180-191907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-180-191907.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Marca, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-he-2018-hua-hen-se-no-bom-tan-sau-CR7-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\">Ronaldo ra \u0111i: Ai s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Real?</span><br>\r\nChia tay Cristiano Ronaldo, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ef1 ph\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1581","checkdouble":"191925"}]}